casebody.data:
Marhlau BELIZAIRE, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
The STATE of Florida, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-1569 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. SEPTEMBER 15, 2017 LOGUE, SCALES and LINDSEY, JJ., concur.

Following review of the petition for belated appeal and the State's response thereto, it is ordered that said petition is hereby denied.
